# 3. Data Loading: Implemented a robust multi-pass CSV reader to handle various delimiters (sep/decimal) 
#    without manual intervention, reducing failure-induced re-runs.
# 4. Preprocessing: Used ColumnTransformer with SimpleImputer (median) and StandardScaler. 
#    Standardization ensures faster convergence for linear solvers, reducing total computation time.
# 5. Resource Management: Set n_jobs=1 for the classifier to ensure predictable, serial energy 
#    consumption suitable for constrained CPU environments.
